함께 고민하고 해결책을 찾아나갈 수 있으신 분\"]}',NULL,NULL,'2024-09-12 01:24:20',1),(537,238205,'{\"id\": 238205, \"title\": \"Acoustical Engineer\", \"preferred\": [\"• Bachelor’s or Master degree of electrical engineering, acoustic engineering or physics required.\", \"• Experience or knowledge in the acoustic design, analysis and measurement required.\", \"• Experience in automotive engineering preferred.\", \"• Experience in software design, development preferred.\"], \"work_info\": [\"Acoustic engineer supports audio system design, conducts audio performance evaluation and tuning of vehicle audio system to achieve Bose premium sound.\"], \"qualifications\": [\"• Support audio system design at concept stage\", \"• Conduct audio system performance evaluation at concept stage. Complete concept car audio tuning and get both internal and customer agreement.\", \"• Support speaker layout/package activities during development\", \"• Conduct audio tuning of prototype vehicles at customer site and get agreement of both internal to Bose and customer.\", \"• Documentation/reporting to internal and customer\", \"• Conduct audits of production vehicles to make sure the acoustic performance are reproduced as intended.\", \"• Conduct component level acoustic evaluation as needed.\", \"• Submit required documents in related to activities above both internal and to customer.\", \"• Attend design review to confirm audio performance as needed.\", \"• Support our technology event – mainly conduct technical demonstration\", \"• In vehicle and bench testing of amplifier function verification\", \"[Key Competencies and Skills]\", \"• Customer orientation\", \"Demonstrates a commitment to understand, meet, and exceed the needs of those who can benefit from Bose products and services.\", \"• Communication\", \"Clearly conveys information and ideas through a variety of media to individuals or groups in a manner that engages the audience and helps them understand and retain the message. Fluent in oral and