stomer orientation\", \"o Demonstrate commitment to understand, meet, and exceed the needs of those who can benefit from Bose products and services.\", \"• Communication\", \"o Clearly convey information and ideas through a variety of media to individuals or groups in a manner that engages the audience and helps them understand and retain the message\", \"o Capable of consolidating complex issues (technical and customer management) in concise and factual manner to internal and external stakeholders.\", \"• Critical thinking\", \"o Think clearly, supported by facts, logic, and solid judgment.\", \"o Accurately identify the core issues and perspectives that are central to the decision or problem.\", \"o Use multiple perspectives to identify likely unintended consequences.\", \"• Technical knowledge\", \"o Have achieved a satisfactory level of technical and professional skill or knowledge in position-related areas.\", \"o Understand current technical trends in the areas of expertise.\", \"• Conflict management\", \"o Deal effectively with others in an antagonistic situation.\", \"o Use appropriate interpersonal styles and methods to reduce tension or conflict.\", \"[Education]\", \"• Required BS/BA in Software or Electrical Engineering\", \"• Master’s degree is preferred\"]}',NULL,NULL,'2024-09-12 01:24:20',1),(539,238210,'{\"id\": 238210, \"title\": \"Software Engineering Project Manager\", \"preferred\": [\"• Strong documentation and writing skills especially customer requirements and software design\", \"• Adequate knowledge of reading schematics and data sheets for peripheral components\", \"• Good to have Autosar, Hardware, Audio and DSP knowledge\", \"＞ 5 years experience work on Korea OEM project from concept to SOP\", \"• Communication skills with English and Korean (business level)\", \"• Good time management skills\", \"• Self-motivated and able to work independently.\", \"• PMP is a plus.\", \"• Strong problem-solving skills.\", \"• Bachelor degree required,